snippet.title: Legend of Keepers Return of the Goddess DLC - Official Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2021
snippet.description:
As revealed during Guerrilla Collective 2021, the reverse dungeon crawler, Legend of Keepers, is getting its first DLC with Return of the Goddess. The Return of the Goddess DLC brings a new master, new environment, new monsters and more. Check out the trailer for a look at what to expect including gameplay and more for the DLC, available in Q3 2021.

#IGN #Gaming #SummerOfGaming
